<p>Pages with proper schema markup score significantly higher on citability because AI systems can extract structured facts programmatically rather than parsing unstructured text.</p>
<h3>6. Content Freshness</h3>
<p>AI systems are biased toward recently updated content. An <a href="https://ahrefs.com/blog/">Ahrefs study</a> found that AI assistants prefer content that is 25.7% fresher than the URLs appearing in traditional organic search results. Perplexity shows the strongest freshness bias among all AI platforms.</p>
<p>What this means for your citability score:
- Update high-value pages quarterly with fresh data and examples
- Include publication dates and "last updated" timestamps
- Remove or refresh outdated statistics and screenshots
- Add current-year references where relevant</p>
<p>Our guide on <a href="/blog/update-old-blog-posts/">updating old blog posts</a> covers the full refresh process.</p>
