<h3>DIY Citability Audit Checklist</h3>
<p>Score each factor from 0 to 10. Total your score out of 80, then convert to a percentage.</p>
<ul>
<li>[ ] <strong>Structure (0-10):</strong> Clear headings, lists, tables, answer-first format</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Factual density (0-10):</strong> Specific stats, named sources, quantified claims</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Answer format (0-10):</strong> Direct answers within first 2 sentences per section</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>E-E-A-T signals (0-10):</strong> Author bylines, credentials, external citations</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Schema markup (0-10):</strong> FAQPage, Article, HowTo, or relevant schemas present</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Freshness (0-10):</strong> Updated within last 90 days, current-year references</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Crawler access (0-10):</strong> GPTBot, PerplexityBot, Googlebot all allowed</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Semantic depth (0-10):</strong> Covers topic thoroughly with related subtopics</li>
</ul>
